|10|        │ │ │ │ └─SORT               |                      |36      |222         |
|11|        │ │ │ │   └─HASH JOIN        |                      |36      |215         |
|12|        │ │ │ │     ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|household_demographics|34      |14          |
|13|        │ │ │ │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN|customer              |1000    |112         |
|14|        │ │ │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |catalog_returns       |1500    |159         |
|15|        │ │ └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET  |date_dim              |1       |16          |
|16|        │ └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET    |customer_demographics |1       |16          |
|17|        └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET      |call_center           |1       |16          |
